headline: Smurfit Westrock (NYSE:SW): Revisiting Valuation After a Tough Year for the Share Price
summary: Smurfit Westrock stock reacts to recent performance Smurfit Westrock (SW) has been a tricky ride lately, with the stock sliding about 31% year to date even as revenue and net income keep grinding higher in a tough packaging market.
